<fn-group>
  <fn id="fn1">
    <label>1</label><p>Recovery of unbiased estimates of the 21-cm power
    spectrum requires that the field of view of the foreground model
    encompasses the region of sky from which instrument-weighted
    foregrounds contribute significantly to the observed data
    (<xref alt="Burba et al., 2023" rid="ref-burbaU003A2023" ref-type="bibr">Burba
    et al., 2023</xref>).</p>
  </fn>
  <fn id="fn2">
    <label>2</label><p><monospace>BayesEoR</monospace> uses a routine
    from the Matrix Algebra for GPU and Multicore Architectures
    (<ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://icl.utk.edu/magma/">MAGMA</ext-link>)
    library which allows for the use of matrices with a memory footprint
    larger than the available RAM on a GPU.</p>
  </fn>
</fn-group>
